Class Jetty10WebSocketHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.socket.adapter.jetty.Jetty10WebSocketHandlerAdapter

  • @WebSocket
public class Jetty10WebSocketHandlerAdapter
extends Object
    Identical to JettyWebSocketHandlerAdapter, only excluding the onWebSocketFrame method, since the Frame argument has moved to a different package in Jetty 10.
